EXPLANATION OF INVOLVEMENT: SCOTT ROSE IS AN EMPLOYEE OF SHEPPARD PRATT HEALTH SYSTEM INC, AN ORGANIZATION RELATED TO WAY STATION INC. GORDON ROTHROCK IS AN EMPLOYEE OF WAY STATION INC.ANTONIO SIMPKINS IS A TRUSTEE OF WAY STATION INC.

WAY STATION FOUNDATION INC CEASED OPERATIONS DURING THE FISCAL YEAR AND DISTRIBUTED ALL ITS ASSETS TO WAY STATION INC. AS OF FEBRUARY 15, 2023.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION B, LINE 11B
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THE 990 IS PREPARED BY WAY STATION STAFF FROM INTERNAL RECORDS, REVIEWED BY SC&H TAX ADVISORY SERVICES AND SHEPPARD PRATT'S CFO AND DIRECTOR OF FINANCE PRIOR TO COMPLETION. A FINAL DRAFT IS SENT TO BOARD MEMBERS IN ADVANCE OF FILING WITH A COVER MEMO HIGHLIGHTING KEY INFORMATION AND CHANGES FROM THE PRIOR YEAR.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION B, LINE 12C
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THE ORGANIZATION REQUIRES ALL TRUSTEES AND KEY EXECUTIVE PERSONNEL TO COMPLETE A CONFLICT OF INTEREST QUESTIONNAIRE ANNUALLY. THE COMPLETED QUESTIONNAIRES ARE REVIEWED BY THE CFO OF SHEPPARD PRATT WHO SUMMARIZES THE REPORTED CONFLICTS. THIS INFORMATION IS THEN PRESENTED TO THE CEO & THE CHAIRMAN OF THE BOARD FOR REVIEW. IF IN THE NORMAL COURSE OF CONDUCTING A BOARD MEETING, AN AGENDA TOPIC IS DETERMINED TO PRESENT A CONFLICT OF INTEREST, THE INTERESTED BOARD MEMBER IS REQUIRED TO DISQUALIFY HIM OR HERSELF FROM ANY FURTHER DISCUSSION ON THE MATTER. THE CHAIRPERSON WILL SELECT A DISINTERESTED PERSON TO INVESTIGATE ALTERNATIVES TO THE TRANSACTION THAT POSES THE POTENTIAL CONFLICT. IF AFTER EXERCISING DUE DILIGENCE THE BOARD DETERMINES THAT IT'S UNABLE TO SECURE A MORE ADVANTAGEOUS TRANSACTION WITH AN ENTITY THAT WOULD NOT GIVE RISE TO A CONFLICT OF INTEREST, THE BOARD WILL DETERMINE WHETHER OR NOT TO ENTER INTO THE TRANSACTION, IF IT IS IN THE BEST INTEREST OF THE ORGANIZATION.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION B, LINE 15
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THE ORGANIZATION DOES NOT PAY COMPENSATION.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION C, LINE 19
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: FINANCIAL STATEMENTS, GOVERNING DOCUMENTS, AND OTHER POLICIES INCLUDING THE CONFLICT OF INTEREST POLICY ARE AVAILABLE UPON REQUEST.
THERE WERE NO CHANGES TO THESE PROCEDURES FROM THE PRIOR YEAR.
